o, MI.[5] "Product Information. Firmagon (degarelix)." Ferring Pharmaceuticals Inc, Tarrytown, NY.[6] "Product Information. Lupron (leuprolide)." TAP Pharmaceuticals Inc, Deerfield, IL.[7] "Product Information. Eligard (leuprolide)." Sanofi Winthrop Pharmaceuticals, New York, NY.[8] "Product Information. Plenaxis (abarelix)." Praecis Pharmaceuticals Inc, Waltham, MA.', 1767369485);
